name: Somette_Brown_Weathered_2-door_Cabinet
reviews: Sadly, though it was packaged extremely well it arrived damaged. The carrier clearly ran into the carton with something and broke the mirror in one door. It is beautiful though and OS is working to get a replacement mirror. It looks exactly like the online image. I hope to put it in my bath for storage. :)
The quLity of the piece is outstanding. It fit perfect in our entryway. The colors are true to the picture on the site. The knobs are a great accent.
description: Accent your home's decor with this stylish Somette cabinet. The brown color and painted, glass finish of this rectangle cabinet will bring a refined feel to your home. Made of MDF, wood and glass, this cabinet has a solid construction built to last.
